  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BULLET TIME</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/47e03a3aa920367aae7506ee59c1973a.poster.avif?t=1736575655\" width=660 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/47e03a3aa920367aae7506ee59c1973a.webm?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/47e03a3aa920367aae7506ee59c1973a.mp4?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔵 Activate Bullet Time to execute thrilling kills and see the Iron Heads' guts explode, the raw smell of iron, lead, and glory. Each blast in Bullet Time is a brutal spectacle, with Iron Heads ripped apart in the jaws of the T-Rex Titan Beast.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>JETPACK</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/3a086ae80c9fc83b0b257159081f5561.poster.avif?t=1736575655\" width=660 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/3a086ae80c9fc83b0b257159081f5561.webm?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/3a086ae80c9fc83b0b257159081f5561.mp4?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔵 Blast into the sky with Jetpack and shooting enemies down below, dodging all 12 missiles from Bluto's mech, seeing crisp trails of blazing heat and smoke passing by from the bazooka.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SKILL TREE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/d3003acebeaf6296874ab9eed9a00a5f.poster.avif?t=1736575655\" width=660 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/d3003acebeaf6296874ab9eed9a00a5f.webm?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/d3003acebeaf6296874ab9eed9a00a5f.mp4?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔵 Craft your own legend. Slaughter Titan Cobra and thousands of Eyeball Spiders from a selection of 20+ abilities and 60+ upgrades, mastering auto-aim, unleashing full damage, unlocking unlimited Bullet Time and Jetpack.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WEAPONS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/5b2fd2febdb7eec8e51d7717516cbba9.poster.avif?t=1736575655\" width=660 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/5b2fd2febdb7eec8e51d7717516cbba9.webm?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/5b2fd2febdb7eec8e51d7717516cbba9.mp4?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔵 Burn thousands of Rats alive with the Flamethrower. Equip and upgrade the deadliest weapons: Missiles, Gatling Gun, Katana, and Bazooka, to rain hell full of lead for those who dare stand in your way.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ARMOR</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/8c67fa0e78989718f0dc6c035cd7c72d.poster.avif?t=1736575655\" width=660 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/8c67fa0e78989718f0dc6c035cd7c72d.webm?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/8c67fa0e78989718f0dc6c035cd7c72d.mp4?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔵 Customize your armor from head to toe, with each piece enhancing and increasing your Bullet Time, Firepower, or Jetpack skills. In full Titan Tech armor made with the latest Cyborg City technology available, Samurai's katana won’t leave a scratch.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BOSSES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/4bfe2d7d311316a43092ba1e64ced47c.poster.avif?t=1736575655\" width=660 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/4bfe2d7d311316a43092ba1e64ced47c.webm?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/4bfe2d7d311316a43092ba1e64ced47c.mp4?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔵 Face against Rig Lord's Beast, a raging T-Rex with a Bite that shreds steel and a Tail Whip that flattens everything in its path. Hordes of Rats and Spiders pour in like a living flood, the massive Titan Cobra shooting green laser beams, Samurai’s katana slicing through the air, and missile mech Bluto—the ultimate threat to Cyborg City.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PURE COMBAT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/4fd19bc6d7464b57da30d25ec35cfdd8.poster.avif?t=1736575655\" width=660 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/4fd19bc6d7464b57da30d25ec35cfdd8.webm?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/4fd19bc6d7464b57da30d25ec35cfdd8.mp4?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔵 No Point A-to-B grind or fetch tasks, dive straight to the action.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE WORLD</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/4d0f179b3242bbf50312fee6de11842c.poster.avif?t=1736575655\" width=660 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/4d0f179b3242bbf50312fee6de11842c.webm?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/4d0f179b3242bbf50312fee6de11842c.mp4?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Year 2225. New York.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>The Sun has burned the oceans dry. The air is poisoned and no longer clean. Fresh water is a currency worth more than life, fought over with blood and bullets. Every day is a brutal fight, for just a little.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Nations fell long ago, leaving towers of high-tech cities made of steel and circuits. Flesh replaced with metal, minds wired with code, to compete against nature, against AI, and against others just as desperate. And you've heard the stories. There’s a place. A hope, a dream. </i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>They call it, </i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Cyborg City.</i></strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TORCH-SHAPED CYBORG CITY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/2f844a9c4cf55bea1d604413b7a24113.poster.avif?t=1736575655\" width=660 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/2f844a9c4cf55bea1d604413b7a24113.webm?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/2f844a9c4cf55bea1d604413b7a24113.mp4?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cyborg City is about 17 times the Statue of Liberty's height, with 7 Zones:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔵 <strong>Zone 0:</strong> The Cyborg City Council HQ, the nerve center where the City Ruler controls everything. The only place in the world where you can see green grass and trees, with water-flowing fountains.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔵 Zone 1:</strong> Residential area for citizens, with housing, schools, and hospitals, and luxurious residentials for VIP only.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔵 Zone 2:</strong> The Entertainment District, full of stadiums, a gladiator arena, malls, clubs, theaters, and restaurants.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔵 Zone 3:</strong> Manufacturing artificial water, food, and precious air—resources that citizens of Cyborg City have to pay for to live there.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔵 Zone 4:</strong> Titan Factories, where the city's most advanced cyborgs and weapon systems are created.<strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔵 Zone 5:</strong> Medusa's Cathedral overlooks the Common Factories and Black Market, where secret deals take place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔵 Zone 6:</strong> Under the Statue of Liberty's feet are a scrapyard and shipyard crawling with Iron Heads, surrounded by oil rigs and sewer systems.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BULLET TIME</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/47e03a3aa920367aae7506ee59c1973a.poster.avif?t=1736575655\" width=660 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/47e03a3aa920367aae7506ee59c1973a.webm?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/47e03a3aa920367aae7506ee59c1973a.mp4?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔵 Activate Bullet Time to execute thrilling kills and see the Iron Heads' guts explode, the raw smell of iron, lead, and glory. Each blast in Bullet Time is a brutal spectacle, with Iron Heads ripped apart in the jaws of the T-Rex Titan Beast.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>JETPACK</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/3a086ae80c9fc83b0b257159081f5561.poster.avif?t=1736575655\" width=660 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/3a086ae80c9fc83b0b257159081f5561.webm?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/3a086ae80c9fc83b0b257159081f5561.mp4?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔵 Blast into the sky with Jetpack and shooting enemies down below, dodging all 12 missiles from Bluto's mech, seeing crisp trails of blazing heat and smoke passing by from the bazooka.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SKILL TREE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/d3003acebeaf6296874ab9eed9a00a5f.poster.avif?t=1736575655\" width=660 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/d3003acebeaf6296874ab9eed9a00a5f.webm?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/d3003acebeaf6296874ab9eed9a00a5f.mp4?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔵 Craft your own legend. Slaughter Titan Cobra and thousands of Eyeball Spiders from a selection of 20+ abilities and 60+ upgrades, mastering auto-aim, unleashing full damage, unlocking unlimited Bullet Time and Jetpack.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WEAPONS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/5b2fd2febdb7eec8e51d7717516cbba9.poster.avif?t=1736575655\" width=660 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/5b2fd2febdb7eec8e51d7717516cbba9.webm?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/5b2fd2febdb7eec8e51d7717516cbba9.mp4?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔵 Burn thousands of Rats alive with the Flamethrower. Equip and upgrade the deadliest weapons: Missiles, Gatling Gun, Katana, and Bazooka, to rain hell full of lead for those who dare stand in your way.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ARMOR</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/8c67fa0e78989718f0dc6c035cd7c72d.poster.avif?t=1736575655\" width=660 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/8c67fa0e78989718f0dc6c035cd7c72d.webm?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/8c67fa0e78989718f0dc6c035cd7c72d.mp4?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔵 Customize your armor from head to toe, with each piece enhancing and increasing your Bullet Time, Firepower, or Jetpack skills. In full Titan Tech armor made with the latest Cyborg City technology available, Samurai's katana won’t leave a scratch.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BOSSES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/4bfe2d7d311316a43092ba1e64ced47c.poster.avif?t=1736575655\" width=660 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/4bfe2d7d311316a43092ba1e64ced47c.webm?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/4bfe2d7d311316a43092ba1e64ced47c.mp4?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔵 Face against Rig Lord's Beast, a raging T-Rex with a Bite that shreds steel and a Tail Whip that flattens everything in its path. Hordes of Rats and Spiders pour in like a living flood, the massive Titan Cobra shooting green laser beams, Samurai’s katana slicing through the air, and missile mech Bluto—the ultimate threat to Cyborg City.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PURE COMBAT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/4fd19bc6d7464b57da30d25ec35cfdd8.poster.avif?t=1736575655\" width=660 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/4fd19bc6d7464b57da30d25ec35cfdd8.webm?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/4fd19bc6d7464b57da30d25ec35cfdd8.mp4?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔵 No Point A-to-B grind or fetch tasks, dive straight to the action.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE WORLD</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/4d0f179b3242bbf50312fee6de11842c.poster.avif?t=1736575655\" width=660 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/4d0f179b3242bbf50312fee6de11842c.webm?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/4d0f179b3242bbf50312fee6de11842c.mp4?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Year 2225. New York.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>The Sun has burned the oceans dry. The air is poisoned and no longer clean. Fresh water is a currency worth more than life, fought over with blood and bullets. Every day is a brutal fight, for just a little.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Nations fell long ago, leaving towers of high-tech cities made of steel and circuits. Flesh replaced with metal, minds wired with code, to compete against nature, against AI, and against others just as desperate. And you've heard the stories. There’s a place. A hope, a dream. </i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>They call it, </i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Cyborg City.</i></strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TORCH-SHAPED CYBORG CITY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/2f844a9c4cf55bea1d604413b7a24113.poster.avif?t=1736575655\" width=660 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/2f844a9c4cf55bea1d604413b7a24113.webm?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929890/extras/2f844a9c4cf55bea1d604413b7a24113.mp4?t=1736575655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cyborg City is about 17 times the Statue of Liberty's height, with 7 Zones:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔵 <strong>Zone 0:</strong> The Cyborg City Council HQ, the nerve center where the City Ruler controls everything. The only place in the world where you can see green grass and trees, with water-flowing fountains.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔵 Zone 1:</strong> Residential area for citizens, with housing, schools, and hospitals, and luxurious residentials for VIP only.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔵 Zone 2:</strong> The Entertainment District, full of stadiums, a gladiator arena, malls, clubs, theaters, and restaurants.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔵 Zone 3:</strong> Manufacturing artificial water, food, and precious air—resources that citizens of Cyborg City have to pay for to live there.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔵 Zone 4:</strong> Titan Factories, where the city's most advanced cyborgs and weapon systems are created.<strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔵 Zone 5:</strong> Medusa's Cathedral overlooks the Common Factories and Black Market, where secret deals take place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔵 Zone 6:</strong> Under the Statue of Liberty's feet are a scrapyard and shipyard crawling with Iron Heads, surrounded by oil rigs and sewer systems.</p>",
